## ZBF with NAT on CSR1000v

Modify ZBF to allow SSH from 208.8.8.102

~~~
!@UTM-PH
conf t
 no  ip access-list extended ALLOW-SSH
 ip access-list extended ALLOW-SSH
  permit tcp host 208.8.8.102  host 11.11.11.101 eq 22
 !
 class-map type inspect match-any CM-ALLOW-SSH
  match access-group name ALLOW-SSH
 !
 zone-pair security ZP-OUTIN source OUTSIDE dest INSIDE
  no service-policy type inspect PM-OUTIN
 !
 no policy-map type inspect PM-OUTIN
 policy-map type inspect PM-OUTIN
  class type inspect CM-ALLOW-SSH
   inspect
  class type inspect CM-OUTIN
   drop log
  class class-default
   drop log
 !
 zone-pair security ZP-OUTIN source OUTSIDE dest INSIDE
  service-policy type inspect PM-OUTIN
  end
~~~
  
NOTES: 
- FW-ACL SPECIFY INSIDE LOCAL, 
- SSH USE NAT PUB IP
- ZONEPAIR NEEDS TO REMOVE POLICY THE REMOVE POLICY



